{"tid":627654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"BBC年度風雲人物法拉獲獎","createTime":"2018-04-13T07:07:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T07:50:40.000Z","uid":26769,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7647c2a6cc03153a63d2d99f899f2f3261a131c6","tid":627654,"uid":26769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T07:07:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171218/640_0fdb4c5e35b834be1e16893842a5ae53.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171218%2F640_0fdb4c5e35b834be1e16893842a5ae53.jpg&h=0eb0c6f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171218/640_5eefe0929e0c6025ac465c3820e8e31a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171218%2F640_5eefe0929e0c6025ac465c3820e8e31a.jpg&h=c2ccfd61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由英國國家廣播公司主辦的年度英國體壇風雲人物獎(Sports Personality of the Year Award)今天凌晨正式揭曉，由世錦賽1萬公尺冠軍法拉Mo Farah拿下。<br />\n <br />\n現年34歲法拉，擊敗另外11名入圍者獲獎，獎項由網路投票選出，入圍該獎項運動員須是英國籍或長期居住在英國，並時常在英國參加比賽運動員，這是自2002年以來，再度出現長跑運動員獲獎。<br />\n <br />\n法拉總計獲得83524票，第2名的北愛爾蘭重機賽選手瑞亞Jonathan Rea排名第2，相差不到3千票。(陳國偉／綜合報導)"},{"pid":"d9ecea2965cbe1f85303ec49cfcd7147402cd811","tid":627654,"uid":179859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T07:40:09.000Z","msg":"以為陳法拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb28c8b3776aa1e2637a2d15c4706e98fbbfba9b","tid":627654,"uid":127146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T07:50:40.000Z","msg":"where is my fala<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}